  <thing id="sSorAbber" name="Aberrate" description="The caster transforms one creature into an aberration.\n\nThe subject&apos;s form twists and mutates into a hideous mockery of itself. The subject&apos;s type changes to aberration, and it gains a +1 natural armor bonus to AC (due to the toughening and twisting of the flesh) for every four levels the caster has, up to a maximum of +5.\n\n{b}Special Component:{/b} Fiend: The caster must be an outsider from the Lower Planes to cast this spell." compset="Spell" summary="Subject becomes an abberation.">
