  <thing id="sClrWrBlig" name="Wretched Blight" description="The caster calls up unholy power to smite his enemies.\nThe power takes the form of a soul-chilling mass of clawing darkness.\nOnly good and neutral (not evil) creatures are harmed by the spell.\nThe spell deals 1d8 pts. of damage per caster level (maximum 15d8) to good creatures and renders them stunned for 1d4 rounds.\nA successful Fortitude save reduces damage to half and negates the stunning effect.\nThe spell deals only half damage to creatures that are neither evil nor good, and they are not stunned.\nSuch creatures can reduce the damage in half again (down to one-quarter of the roll) with a successful Reflex save." compset="Spell" summary="Deals 1d8 damage/level in 20-ft. radius and stuns foes for 1d4 rounds.">
