  <thing id="sSorDrWord" name="Dread Word" description="The caster speaks a single unique word of pure malevolence&#151;a powerful utterance from the Dark Speech (see Chapter 2).\nThe word is so foul that it harms the very soul of one that hears it.\nThe utterance of a dread word causes one subject within range to take 1d3 points of Charisma drain.\nThe power of this spell protects the caster from the damaging effects of both hearing and knowing the word.\nTo attempt to speak this unique word without using this spell means instant death (and no effect, because the caster dies before she gets the entire word out)." compset="Spell" summary="1d3 Cha drain on one target.">
