  <thing id="gAgony" name="Agony (Liquid Pain)" description="{b}Addiction:{/b} Extreme\n{b}Type/DC:{/b} Ingested/ 18\n{b}Price:{/b} 200 gp / (2-5 times the price where banned)\n{b}Alchemy DC:{/b} 25\n{b}Description:{/b}\n\nThis thick, reddish liquid is the distilled essence of pain, captured using special spells or items (see the Pain as Power section of Chapter 2). It is highly sought after by outsiders.\n{b}Initial Effect:{/b} User is stunned for 1d4+1 rounds and can take only partial actions for 1d6 minutes after that.\n{b}Secondary Effect:{/b} 1d4+1 enhancement bonus to Charisma for 1d10+50 minutes.\n{b}Side Effects:{/b} Feelings of intense pleasure last for 1d4 hours. Overdose: If more than one dose is taken in a 24-hour period, the user immediately falls unconscious for 1d4 hours (Fort DC 18 negates).\n\n{b}Power Component:{/b} Pain in distilled liquid form (see Pain as Power in Chapter 2), as extracted by certain spells or items, automatically increases the effective caster level of a single spell by +2. This increase doesn&#146;t stack with previous applications of liquid pain or any other such bonuses to effective caster level.\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nTable 3&#150;4: Addictions\nAddiction Rating              Fort DC     Satiation                             Damage\nNegligible                                 4             1 day                 1d3&#150;2 Dex (can be 0)\nLow                                           6           10 days               1d3 Dex\nMedium                                  10             5 days               1d4 Dex, 1d4 Wis\nHigh                                         14             2 days                1d6 Dex, 1d6 Wis, 1d2 Con\nExtreme                                 25             1 day                   1d6 Dex, 1d6 Wis, 1d6 Con\nVicious                                   36             1 day                   1d8 Dex. 1d8 Wis, 1d6 Con, 1d6 Str\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------" compset="Gear" stacking="merge">
