    <fieldval field="gCost" value="200"/>
    <usesource source="BoVD"/>
    <tag group="gType" tag="Drugs" name="Drugs" abbrev="Drug"/>
    <tag group="Helper" tag="GearNoSize"/>
    </thing>
  <thing id="gBaccaran" name="Baccaran" description="{b}Addiction:{/b} Low\n{b}Type/DC:{/b} Ingested DC 14\n{b}Price:{/b} 10 gp / (2-5 times the price where banned)\n{b}Alchemy DC:{/b} 20\n{b}Description:{/b}\n\n{b}Baccaran:{/b} This pasty substance is dried and kept as a powder or sometimes left as a paste. The ingredients are numerous and difficult to obtain.\n{b}Initial Effect:{/b} 1d4 points of Strength damage.\n{b}Secondary Effect:{/b} 1d4+1 enhancement bonus toWisdom for 1d10+15 minutes.\n{b}Side Effects:{/b} Those under the effect of baccaran take a &#150;4 circumstance penalty on saving throws involving illusions for 2d4 hours after using this mild hallucinogen.\n{b}Overdose:{/b} If more than one dose is taken in a 24-hour period, the user immediately takes 2d6 points of damage and the side effect is doubled.\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nTable 3&#150;4: Addictions\nAddiction Rating              Fort DC     Satiation                             Damage\nNegligible                                 4             1 day                 1d3&#150;2 Dex (can be 0)\nLow                                           6           10 days               1d3 Dex\nMedium                                  10             5 days               1d4 Dex, 1d4 Wis\nHigh                                         14             2 days                1d6 Dex, 1d6 Wis, 1d2 Con\nExtreme                                 25             1 day                   1d6 Dex, 1d6 Wis, 1d6 Con\nVicious                                   36             1 day                   1d8 Dex. 1d8 Wis, 1d6 Con, 1d6 Str\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------" compset="Gear" stacking="merge">
