  <thing id="gDevilweed" name="Devilweed" description="{b}Addiction:{/b} Low\n{b}Type/DC:{/b} Inhaled 15\n{b}Price:{/b} 6 gp / (2-5 times the price where banned)\n{b}Alchemy DC:{/b} 20\n{b}Description:{/b}\n\n{b}Devilweed:{/b} Leaves from the wyssin plant are dried and rolled into a tobaccolike substance and smoked.\n{b}Initial Effect:{/b} 1 point ofWisdom damage.\n{b}Secondary Effect:{/b} The smoker gains a +2 alchemical bonus to Strength for 1d3 hours.\n{b}Side Effects:{/b} A creature under the effect of devilweed is easily confused and acts skittish (treat as shaken).\n{b}Overdose:{/b} None.\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nTable 3&#150;4: Addictions\nAddiction Rating              Fort DC     Satiation                             Damage\nNegligible                                 4             1 day                  1d3&#150;2 Dex (can be 0)\nLow                                           6           10 days                1d3 Dex\nMedium                                  10             5 days                1d4 Dex, 1d4 Wis\nHigh                                         14             2 days                1d6 Dex, 1d6 Wis, 1d2 Con\nExtreme                                 25             1 day                   1d6 Dex, 1d6 Wis, 1d6 Con\nVicious                                   36             1 day                   1d8 Dex. 1d8 Wis, 1d6 Con, 1d6 Str\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------" compset="Gear">
