  <thing id="sCORFangVa" name="Fangs of the Vampire King" description="The caster grows vampire-like fangs that allow him to make bite attacks with an attack bonus of +10 plus the caster&#146;s Strength modifier.  The caster&#146;s bite attack deals 1d6 points of damage and 1 point of Constitution damage.\n\n{b}Corruption Cost:{/b} 1d6 points of Strength damage." compset="Spell" summary="Caster gains bite attack with +10 bonus that deals 1d6 damage and 1 Con damage.">
