  <thing id="cdBestial" name="Bestial" description="Bestial Domain\n{b}Deities:{/b} Karaan, Yeenoghu.\n{b}Granted Power:{/b} Character gains the scent extraordinary ability.\n\n{b}Bestial Domain Spells{/b}\n{b}1{/b} &#150; {i}Magic Fang.{/i} One natural weapon of subject creature gets +1 bonus on attack and damage rolls.\n{b}2{/b} &#150; {i}Bull&#146;s Strength.{/i} Subject gains 1d4+1 Str for 1 hr./level.\n{b}3{/b} &#150; {i}Greater Magic Fang.{/i} One natural weapon of subject creature gets +1 bonus on attack and damage rolls per 3 caster levels (max +5).\n{b}4{/b} &#150; {i}Claws of the Savage.{/i} Subject gains claws that deal damage based on size.\n{b}5{/b} &#150; {i}Charm Monster.{/i} Makes monster believe it is your character&#146;s ally.\n{b}6{/b} &#150; {i}Hold Monster.{/i} As hold person, but any creature.\n{b}7{/b} &#150; {i}Whirlwind of Teeth.{/i} Creates moving 5-ft./level cylinder that deals 1d8 damage/2 levels each round.\n{b}8{/b} &#150; {i}Spread of Savagery.{/i} Creatures within 10 ft./level become hostile and savage.\n{b}9{/b} &#150; {i}Were-Doom.{/i} 1d4 creatures infected with lycanthropy.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} Book of Vile Darkness, 3.0" compset="ClerDomain" summary="Grants the scent ability." uniqueness="unique">
