  <thing id="sClrConBea" name="Contagion" description="The subject contracts a disease selected from the table below, which strikes immediately (no incubation period). The DC noted is for the subsequent saves (use {i}contagion{/i}&apos;s normal save DC for the initial saving throw).{br}{vert 7}{b}Disease{/b} - {b}DC{/b} - {b}Damage{/b}{br}Blinding sickness - 16 - 1d4 Str*{br}Cackle fever - 16 - 1d6 Wis{br}Filth fever - 12 - 1d3 Dex and 1d3 Con{br}Mindfire - 12 - 1d4 Int{br}Red ache - 15 - 1d6 Str{br}Shakes - 13 - 1d8 Dex{br}Slimy doom - 14 - 1d4 Con{br}{vert 7}* Each time a victim takes 2 or more points of Strength damage from blinding sickness, he or she must make another Fortitude save (using the disease&apos;s save DC) or be permanently blinded." compset="Spell" summary="Infects subject with chosen disease.">
