  <thing id="cdDemonic" name="Demonic" description="{b}Demonic Domain{/b}\n\n{b}Deities:{/b} Demogorgon, Graz&#146;zt, Yeenoghu.\n{b}Granted Power:{/b} Character gains +1 divine bonus on attack and damage rolls for unarmed strikes and attacks with natural weapons.\n\n{b}Demonic Domain Spells{/b}\n{b}1{/b} &#150; {i}Demonflesh.{/i} Caster gains +1 natural armor/5 caster levels.\n{b}2{/b} &#150; {i}Demoncall.{/i} Caster gains +10 on one Knowledge (the planes), Knowledge (arcana), or Knowledge (religion) check.\n{b}3{/b} &#150; {i}Demon Wings.{/i} Caster flies at his land speed.\n{b}4{/b} &#150; {i}Dimensional Anchor.{/i} Bars extradimensional movement.\n{b}5{/b} &#150; {i}Lesser Planar Binding.{/i} Traps outsider until it performs a task.\n{b}6{/b} &#150; {i}Planar Binding.{/i} As lesser planar binding, but up to 16 HD.\n{b}7{/b} &#150; {i}Fiendish Clarity.{/i} Caster sees in even magical darkness, sees invisible up to 60 feet, and can detect good.\n{b}8{/b} &#150; {i}Utterdark.{/i} 100-ft./level radius of darkness that evil creatures can see through.\n{b}9{/b} &#150; {i}Gate.{/i} Connects two planes for travel or summoning." compset="ClerDomain" summary="+1 Atk and Dmg with Natural Weapons and Unarmed Strikes." uniqueness="unique">
