  <thing id="cdDiabolic" name="Diabolic" description="{b}Diabolic Domain{/b}\n\n{b}Deities:{/b} Asmodeus, Baalzebul, Mammon, Mephistopheles.\n{b}Granted Power:{/b} Once per day, character can add her class level as a bonus on a Bluff, Diplomacy, Intimidate, or Sense Motive check.\n\n{b}Diabolic Domain Spells{/b}\n{b}1{/b} &#150; {i}Devil&#146;s Tail.{/i} Caster gains a spiked tail that deals 1d4 damage.\n{b}2{/b} &#150; {i}Devil&#146;s Eye.{/i} Caster can see in even magical darkness, up to 30 ft.\n{b}3{/b} &#150; {i}Devil&#146;s Ego.{/i} Caster gains 1d4+1 Cha and become an outsider.\n{b}4{/b} &#150; {i}Hellfire.{/i} Explosion of brimstone deals 3d6 damage in 5-ft. radius.\n{b}5{/b} &#150; {i}Lesser Planar Binding.{/i} Traps outsider until it performs a task.\n{b}6{/b} &#150; {i}Planar Binding.{/i} As lesser planar binding, but up to 16 HD.\n{b}7{/b} &#150; {i}Hellfire Storm.{/i} Explosion of brimstone deals 5d6 damage in 20-ft. radius.\n{b}8{/b} &#150; {i}Demand.{/i} As sending, plus caster can send suggestion.\n{b}9{/b} &#150; {i}Gate.{/i} Connects two planes for travel or summoning." compset="ClerDomain" summary="1/Day, Add class level as a bonus on a Bluff, Diplo, Intim, or Sense Motive." uniqueness="unique">
