  <thing id="cdPain" name="Pain" description="{b}Pain Domain{/b}\n{b}Deities:{/b} Rallaster, Scahrossar.\n{b}Granted Power:{/b} Character converts damage that he deals in one blow per day into healing for himself, up to 1 point of damage per level.\n\n{b}Pain Domain Spells{/i}\n{b}1{/b} &#150; {i}Angry Ache.{/i} Subject takes &#150;2 penalty on attack rolls.\n{b}2{/b} &#150; {i}Sadism.{/i} For every 10 hp damage caster deals, he gains +1 on attacks, saves, and checks.\n{b}3{/b} &#150; {i}Wrack.{/i} Blinds subject and renders it helpless for 1 round/level, then &#150;2 on attacks, saves, and checks for 3d10 minutes.\n{b}4{/b} &#150; {i}Liquid Pain.{/i} Extracts one dose of liquid pain from tortured victim.\n{b}5{/b} &#150; {i}Thousand Needles.{/i} Piercing needles deal 2d6 damage, and target takes &#150;4 penalty on attacks, saves, and checks.\n{b}6{/b} &#150; {i}Pox.{/i} One creature/level takes 1d4 Con drain.\n{b}7{/b} &#150; {i}Wave of Pain.{/i} Stuns all within cone for 1 round/2 levels.\n{b}8{/b} &#150; {i}Symbol (pain only).{/i} Triggered rune causes pain.\n{b}9{/b} &#150; {i}Eternity of Torture.{/i} Target is rendered helpless, ageless, and has all ability scores except for Con drop to 0.\n\n{b}Source: {/b}Book of Vile Darkness, 3.0" compset="ClerDomain" summary="1/day, convert all dam dealt in a single blow to healing. (up to class level)" uniqueness="unique">
    <usesource source="BoVD"/>
