  <thing id="cDemChaDem" name="Charm Demon" description="A 1st-level demonologist can attempt to charm a chaotic evil outsider, as described in the charm person spell, once per day. The demon does not get to use its spell resistance, though it can make a saving throw as normal (DC 11 + demonologist&apos;s Cha modifier)." compset="ClSpecial" summary="1/day, Charm Demon functioning as a charm person spell.">
