  <thing id="cDemQuasFa" name="Quasit Familar" description="A 2nd-level demonologist gains a quasit as a familiar, whether he wants it or not. If the demonologist already has a familiar, the quasit devours it and takes its place, but the character suffers no experience point loss.  The quasit is treated as a normal familiar, using the class level of the demonologist as the master&apos;s level (see the Familiars section in Chapter 3 of the Player&apos;s Handbook for familiar abilities)." compset="ClSpecial" summary="You gain a--or replace your current-- familar with a Quasit.">
