  <thing id="iFleshshif" name="Fleshshifter Armor" description="Made from the skins of humanoids, this +1 leather armor allows the wearer to produce an effect identical to that of the {i}alter self{/i} spell at will.\n\nCaster Level: 3rd; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, alter self; Market Price: 13,160 gp." compset="MagicArmor">
