  <thing id="iRazorArm" name="Razor Armor" description="Razor Armor: Made of layers and layers of razor-sharp scales, this +2 scale armor deals 2d6 points of slashing damage with a successful grapple check and when the wearer is grappling. The wearer is considered proficient with the razors. Once per day, the wearer can spend a standard action to launch up to six of the razor scales, which fly out from the armor like +1 shuriken.\n\nCaster Level: 3rd; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, magic weapon; Market Price: 5,600 gp." compset="MagicArmor">
