  <thing id="iBlkGBlade" name="Blackguard&apos;s Blade" description="Made of black iron and covered in evil symbols engraved in the blade, this +2 longsword adds +10 damage to the wielder&#146;s smite good ability.\n\nCaster Level: 13th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, unholy blight, creator must be evil; Market Price: 9,515 gp;Weight: 4 lb." compset="MagicWep" summary="+2 Longsword, add +10 dmg with the wielder&apos;s smite good ability.">
