  <thing id="iChaiBlade" name="Chain of Barriers" description="Chain of Barriers: This item is a +1 spiked chain. When commanded with the proper word, however, it expands to become a wall of chains.With a second command word, the chain of barriers reverts to weapon form.\n\nCaster Level: 5th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, wall of chains; Market Price: 29,325 gp; Weight: 15 lb." compset="MagicWep" summary="+1 Spiked Chain, on command expands to a wall of chains and/or back to weapon.">
