  <thing id="iCharnReav" name="Charnal Reaver" description="This +3 dwarven waraxe, usually created by duergar smiths, utterly consumes the physical form of any living creature it slays, requiring a true resurrection spell to bring the creature back to life (raise dead and resurrection will not work).\n\nCaster Level: 9th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, charnel fire; Market Price: 108,330 gp; Weight: 15 lb." compset="MagicWep" summary="+3 Dwarven Waraxe, utterly destroys the remains of those it slays.">
