  <thing id="iSpectArro" name="Spectral Arrow" description="Spectral Arrow: This arrow looks like a +1 arrow, but it is an invisible brilliant energy projectile that bestows two negative levels rather than dealing normal damage.\n\nCaster Level: 17th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, energy drain, gaseous form, invisibility; Market Price: 2,560 gp." compset="MagicWep" summary="+1 Arrow, bestows two negative levels instead of dealing damage.">
