  <thing id="iWarpsword" name="Warpsword" description="This +2 greatsword infects anyone it strikes with warp touch (see Diseases in Chapter 2) if the target fails a Fortitude save (DC 14).\nCaster Level: 9th; Prerequisites: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, contagion, cloak of chaos; Market Price: 78,350 gp; Weight: 10 lb." compset="MagicWep" summary="+2 Greatsword; Infects anyone it strikes with {i}Warp Touch{/i}">
