  <thing id="irWeeping" name="Ring of Weeping" description="This dull gray ring allows the wearer to bestow weeping, crippling sadness by touch.  A humanoid touched by the wearer of a ring of weeping must succeed at a Will save (DC 11) or be incapacitated for 1 round, then take a &#150;3 morale penalty on attack rolls, saving throws, ability checks, and skill checks for 5 rounds. Each time the ring is used to affect a creature, its wearer takes a &#150;1 morale penalty on attack rolls, saving throws, ability checks, and skill checks for 5 rounds.\n\nCaster Level: 5th; Prerequisites: Forge Ring, sorrow; Market Price: 3,000 gp." compset="Ring" summary="Bestows Crippling Sadness by Touch, -3 pen to everything for 5 rounds.">
    <fieldval field="gCost" value="3000"/>
    <usesource source="BoVD"/>
    <tag group="gType" tag="Ring"/>
