  <thing id="irVileSpel" name="Vile Spell Ring" description="If this ring is worn by a spellcaster, 1 point of damage per spell level from each of the caster&#146;s damaging spells is vile damage. If multiple creatures take damage (such as with a fireball spell), each creature takes the vile damage.\n\nCaster Level: 5th; Prerequisites: Forge Ring, vile lance; Market Price: 15,000 gp." compset="Ring" summary="While Worn, adds +1 vile damage/Spell Level of dmging spell being cast.">
