  <thing id="isPestilen" name="Staff of Pestilence" description="This wooden staff is covered in diseased sores that ooze yellow pus. It gives off a horrible odor of rotten flesh, but allows the use of the following spells.\n\n&#149; Contagion (1 charge, DC 16)\n&#149; Insect plague (1 charge, DC 17)\n&#149; Pox(2 charges, DC 19)\n\nCaster Level: 11th; Prerequisites: Craft Staff, contagion, insect plague, pox; Market Price: 70,000 gp;Weight: 5 lb." compset="Staff" summary="A staff with a wide range of sickening spells.">
