  <thing id="ioCoVirVen" name="Collar of Virulent Venom" description="A creature wearing this heavy iron collar gives all of its natural attacks an additional poison attack (Fort DC 20) that deals 1d10 points of Constitution damage as its initial and secondary damage.\n\nCaster Level: 18th; Prerequisites: Craft Wondrous Item, Heighten Spell, poison; Market Price: 138,000 gp; Weight: 3 lb." compset="Wondrous" summary="Wearer deals 1d10 points of Con damage per hit with nat attacks. DC F20 neg">
