  <thing id="ioGemPsyPo" name="Gem of Psychic Poison" description="This gem, when in the possession of a creature, poisons that creature so that anyone casting a mind-affecting or divination spell at the creature is affected with a psychic poison (see Chapter 3) that deals 1d6 points of Intelligence damage as both initial and secondary damage.\n\nCaster Level: 7th; Prerequisites: Craft Wondrous Item, poison area; Market Price: 28,000 gp." compset="Wondrous" summary="Affects anyone casting m-a or div spl is affected with a psychic pois. 1d6 INT." uniqueness="useronce">
