  <thing id="ipElixDkSp" name="Elixir of Dark Speech" description="This allows the imbiber to speak and understand the Dark Speech as if he possessed the feat of the same name. This elixir deals 1 point of Strength damage when used. The speech effect lasts for 10 minutes.\n\nCaster Level: 5th; Prerequisites: Craft Wondrous Item, dread word; Market Price: 750 gp; Weight: 1 lb." compset="OilPotion" summary="Grants Imbiber the Dark Speech feat for 10mins.  Deals 1pt of STR dmg." stacking="merge">
